SIMPLE: neighborly
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Neighborly
<hw>Neigh"bor*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Also written
<ets>neighbourly</ets>.]</ety> <def>Appropriate to the relation of
neighbors; having frequent or familiar intercourse; kind; civil; social;
friendly.</def> -- <def2><pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a neighborly
manner.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Judge if this be <qex>neighborly</qex> dealing.</q>
<rj><qau>Arbuthnot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Neighborship</ent>⟦br⟧
